{"tid":184533,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"［隨便台］[開CAM開台]開台打DEAD BY DAYLIGHT","createTime":"2017-04-03T01:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T02:18:19.000Z","uid":89382,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec6571ccce4184047f1980fb3dc356f2fe963ea","tid":184533,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"Twitch link : <a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/justin_yu_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fjustin_yu_1&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ff6ad1b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/justin_yu_1</a><br />\nSteam link : <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/381210/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F381210%2F&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=dfeb4cf3\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/381210/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.deadbydaylight.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DBD_Standard_Edition.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.deadbydaylight.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2FDBD_Standard_Edition.jpg&h=8dd4f805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDead by daylight呢隻GAME,係一隻4 VS 1既GAME,4個人類一邊維修發電機一邊避開個殺手,維修夠發電機開大門走佬;玩殺手既就係盡量殺D人,唔俾佢地走到佬<br />\n<br />\n可惜,呢隻GAME,外國好多人玩,偏偏淨係香港冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多係身在外國既香港人,都同我講呢隻GAME外國係勁多人玩,普遍香港人個STEAM都設定係香港,所以香港人買左,馬上開GAME,幾乎係肯定冇場,因為香港SER根本冇人,已經真係有玩開GAME既人,都已經轉哂SER去其他國家玩,而依家最多人既SER而又唔會太LAG既地方,係轉去台灣泰國日本哈薩克呢D地方既SER玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HdDRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHdDRQ.jpg&h=300ec0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於係香港開CAM開台而又玩呢隻GAME既人,係得我一個台,所以呢隻GAME官方果邊都俾左呢一件twitch台台主先有既SKIN我,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/16665881_781048895392865_7174868728788210755_o.jpg?oh=77d2297321dacb84b71d369393e79c2b&amp;oe=593238E6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F16665881_781048895392865_7174868728788210755_o.jpg%3Foh%3D77d2297321dacb84b71d369393e79c2b%26oe%3D593238E6&h=385eb1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/16797126_781048898726198_8047297476270724355_o.jpg?oh=2f5a4bf342f0bc469c7ca8774e4a607b&amp;oe=5941D525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F16797126_781048898726198_8047297476270724355_o.jpg%3Foh%3D2f5a4bf342f0bc469c7ca8774e4a607b%26oe%3D5941D525&h=6384d9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/vHoXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FvHoXA.jpg&h=1fb87b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHk7eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHk7eR.jpg&h=f109db8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/隨便台/355532761277816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2F%E9%9A%A8%E4%BE%BF%E5%8F%B0%2F355532761277816&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=33ef3551\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pages/隨便台/355532761277816</a>"},{"pid":"72db0c5171e04118e0684c9bb4942cd71d830192","tid":184533,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1798c164c711b88bff2c300fb8f91853ee774f","tid":184533,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f41ff0a1b9316cbebd1d179f1109f3da71d22f","tid":184533,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo